<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <%- include('./partials/head', {title: "Website: Forgot Password"}); %>
    </head>

    <body>
        <%- include('./partials/header'); %>
        <%- include('./partials/backbutton'); %>
        <div class="container mt-5 main-div">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h3 class="card-title text-center">How to Reset Your Password</h3>
                            <p>If you forgot your password, follow the steps below to reset it. This process involves sending your User ID to our support email. Please read carefully to ensure you can regain access to your account:</p>
                            <div class="alert alert-warning">
                                <strong>Note:</strong> Make sure to have access to your User ID and the email you used to register.
                            </div>
                            <ol>
                                <li><strong>Retrieve Your User ID:</strong> Log in to your account homepage. If you are unable to log in, try recalling your user credentials. Your User ID is available in your profile information on the home page.</li>
                                <li><strong>Send an Email to Support:</strong> Once you have your User ID, compose an email to <a href="mailto:support.tonnslegostore@shop.com">support.tonnslegostore@shop.com</a> with the following details:
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Subject: <strong>Password Reset Request</strong></li>
                                        <li>Body: Include your User ID and state that you need to reset your password.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li><strong>Wait for a Response:</strong> After sending the email, our support team will verify your request. If your request is approved, you will receive an email containing a unique reset code.</li>
                                <li><strong>Enter the Reset Code:</strong> Go to your account home page and find the password reset section. Enter the reset code exactly as it appears in the email.</li>
                                <li><strong>Create a New Password:</strong> Once the reset code is verified, you will be prompted to create a new password. Make sure to choose a strong password for your account security.</li>
                                <li><strong>Complete the Reset:</strong> After successfully creating a new password, you can now log in using your new credentials.</li>
                            </ol>
                            <p>If you encounter any issues during this process, feel free to contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support.tonnslegostore@shop.com">support.tonnslegostore@shop.com</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('./partials/footer'); %>
    </body>
    
</html>
